  <Title>Dark Ages 7.1 patch on 03/14</Title>
  <Type>1</Type>
  <Content>On March 14th, Dark Ages will be updating to version 7.10. The following features will be added.

- Improved security on client-to-server communication.

- A new armor slot will be added to allow players to wear non-combat armors over their combat armors (making non-combat armor visible but still have the attributes  of the combat armor). Examples of non-combat armor are political armors and formal armors.

- The ability points for monsters in Medenia will be increased.

- Additional floors and new monsters will be added to the Cursed Home in Hwarone.

- 3 new quests in Hwarone.
