Coming Soon:
 
Item Shop - Shortly after the patch will be the launch of the Dark Ages Item Shop.  Items sold in the shop will be for looks, i.e. formal armors, holiday armors, pets, effect potions, etc. Items can be purchase using the Kruna currency. Kruna can be purchased, but registered accounts will receive a regular allowance of Kruna. More information will be given about the item shop when the launch date is finalized.
